Package org.drip.json.parser

Class ParseException

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Throwable
      • java.lang.Exception
        • org.drip.json.parser.ParseException
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    public class ParseException
extends java.lang.Exception
    ParseException is an Adaptation of the ParseException Class from the RFC4627 compliant JSON Simple (https://code.google.com/p/json-simple/).

    • Module = Computational Core Module
    • Library = Computation Support
    • Project = RFC-4627 Compliant JSON Encoder/Decoder (Parser)
    • Package = RFC4627 Compliant JSON Message Parser
